

-record xml file name 
used to create the sml response file taht can be used for a silent installation

-silent 
used to run im in silent headless mode. 
for this to work you want to use 
-acceptLicense to get over nagging questions
and
-input  xml response file
to specify the applications you want 
to un(in)stall


-updateAll to yes update All installed apps (as far as the installed IM version allows).
note most of the time this will not move you to a newer major version.
